    {
      "text": "Cross Tantei Monogatari (クロス 探偵 物語) also known as Cross Detective Story  is an adventure game developed and published by WorkJam for the PlayStation and Sega Saturn. It was released only in Japan in 1998.\nThe game was the first to be developed by WorkJam. It was originally released for the Sega Saturn, and was remade for the PlayStation, containing additional features. Upon release, Japanese reviews were positive, but the game was a commercial failure.",
